  "title": "Business Development Associate",
  "description": "<p>If you’re ready to begin a new chapter in your career, this Sales Consultant role could be the ideal starting point. Fresh graduates, ORD personnel, and individuals exploring new opportunities are all welcome.</p>\n<p>Experience isn’t required. You’ll receive full coaching, practical training, and the support you need to develop professionally.</p>\n<h3><strong>Your Responsibilities</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Engaging customers at various events and campaigns</li>\n  <li>Presenting and explaining product features confidently</li>\n  <li>Identifying customer needs and offering appropriate solutions</li>\n  <li>Collaborating with a driven and supportive team</li>\n  <li>Attending ongoing training sessions to enhance your communication and sales skills</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Benefits</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Weekly payout and uncapped commissions</li>\n  <li>Performance incentives</li>\n  <li>Skill-building workshops and leadership development</li>\n  <li>Travel opportunities for learning and exposure</li>\n  <li>A positive team environment</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Why This Role Stands Out</strong></h3>\n<p>You’ll not only gain experience but also develop important interpersonal and communication skills that are valuable in any career. If you’re motivated and willing to learn, you’ll find plenty of opportunities to grow quickly.</p>\n<h3><strong>Apply Now</strong></h3>\n<p>Reach out today to secure a spot. Early applications are prioritised.</p>",
